p.e:
Speed Strike is the coolest
gamer ever born. Forged in
1465 as a greatsword for the
king of Yeetiya, Speed was
the cause of over five million
deaths in The Great Keeyaah
war of 1480. It's final kill was
a wizard named Gunblidumbd
who cursed the sword to be
reborn thousands of years
in the future. Speed was re-
born a human in 2001. He said
his first words immediatly
after being born; "Rad." He
would not  speak for another 4
years when he was properly
taught english. At age 6, he 
was able to create a rift in
space-time by playing a keytar.
